description: Value Gold ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Sensible Asset Management Hong Kong Limited. The fund in co-managed by Value Partners Hong Kong Limited. It invests in the commodity markets. The fund invests in physical gold. It seeks to track the performance of the London Gold Fixing Price in USD. Value Gold ETF was formed on October 29, 2010 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: Value Gold ETF
